OL,5, TV star Richard Mylan has said the     
OL,6, response to his decision to reveal his 
OL,7, 20-year addiction to heroin has been   
OL,8, "incredible".                          
OL,10,FThe Welsh actor, who has been in       
OL,11,Frecovery for 10 years, first spoke out 
OL,12,Fat the weekend in what he recognised   
OL,13,Fcould be a career-wrecking interview.  
OL,15,FThe 48-year-old, who works with south  
OL,16,FWales-based charity Adferiad, now wants
OL,17,Fto help fellow addicts recover.        
OL,19,F"The response has been genuinely       
OL,20,Foverwhelming," he said.                
